'''''Dhalinyaro''''' ( ''Urubyiruko'' ) ni filime yikinamico ya Djiboutian 2017 iyobowe na Lula Ali Ismaïl aho yabaye umuyobozi wa mbere wa firime ya Djiboutian<ref>https://mg.co.za/africa/2020-07-17-meet-lula-ali-ismail-djiboutis-first-lady-of-film/</ref>.  Yakozwe na diregiteri ubwe hamwe na Alexandra Ramniceanu, Jean-Frédéric Samie na Gilles Sandoz kuri  Samawada films<ref>https://cinando.com/en/Film/dhalinyaro_youth_341919/Detail</ref>.  Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Amina Mohamed Ali, Tousmo Mouhoumed Mohamed, na Bilan Samir Moubus mu nshingano zabo<ref name=":0">https://en.unifrance.org/directories/company/359774/samawada-films</ref>.  Niyo filime ya mbere yerekanwe mu mateka ya sinema ya Djibouti yagaragaye bwa mbere muri Nyakanga 2017.  <ref>[http://www.lanationdj.com/cinema-premiere-film-dhalinyaro/ Cinéma : Avant-première du film "Dhalinyaro"], ''The Nation'', 30 July 2017.</ref> <ref>[http://www.lanationdj.com/dhalinyaro-long-metrage-made-in-djibouti/ DHALINYARO: A feature film made-in-Djibouti].</ref>

Filime ikurikira abakobwa batatu bakomoka mubyiciro bitandukanye byubukungu.<ref name=":0" />  Yatewe inkunga na Organisation de la Francophonie, kandi ikorerwa muri Kanada, [[Somaliya]], Ubufaransa na Djibouti<ref>https://www.africatopsuccess.com/lula-ali-ismail-the-first-djiboutian-film-director/</ref>.  Yafashwe amashusho yose muri Djibouti. Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.<ref>https://www.okayafrica.com/how-to-watch-dhalinyaro-djibouti-french-film-director-lula-ali-ismail-interview/</ref>  

